{{!< default}}
<a name="top"></a>
<div class="dahliaOS-be-together-section mdl-typography--text-center">
    <div class="logo-font dahliaOS-slogan">something new</div>
    <div class="logo-font dahliaOS-sub-slogan">dahliaOS is a modern, secure, lightweight and responsive operating
        system, combining the best of GNU/Linux and Fuchsia OS.</div>
    <div align=center>
        <a href="#features"><button
                class="dahlia-dlnow mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-js-ripple-effect">
                Learn More
            </button></a></div>

    <a href="#screens">
        <button class="dahliaOS-fab mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-button--fab mdl-js-ripple-effect">
            <i class="material-icons">expand_more</i>
        </button>
    </a>
</div>
<div class="dahliaOS-screen-section mdl-typography--text-center">
    <a name="screens"></a>
    <div class="mdl-typography--display-1-color-contrast">News</div>
    <div class="dahliaOS-screens">



        <style>
            .demo-card-square.mdl-card {
                width: 320px;
                height: 320px;
                overflow: wrap;
                white-space: normal;

            }

            .demo-card-square>.mdl-card__title {
                color: #fff;

            }
        </style>

        {{#foreach posts}}
        <div class="dahliaOS-tablet dahliaOS-screen blog-entry {{post_class}}">
            <div class="demo-card-square mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
                <div class="mdl-card__title mdl-card--expand" style="background:
                  url('{{#if feature_image}}{{feature_image}}{{else}}{{asset "images/gradient.png"}}{{/if}}') center #ff3d00; background-size:cover; ">
                    <h2 class="mdl-card__title-text">{{primary_tag.name}} ● {{title}} ● {{date published_at format="Do of MMMM, YYYY"}}</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">
                    {{excerpt}}
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
                    <a class="mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect"
                        href="{{url}}">
                        Read More
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/foreach}}

        <div class="dahliaOS-tablet dahliaOS-screen">
            <div class="demo-card-square mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
                <div class="mdl-card__title mdl-card--expand" style="background:
                  url('{{asset "images/gradient.png"}}') center left 15% no-repeat #ff3d00;">
                    <h2 class="mdl-card__title-text">Community ● We've been featured on Distrowatch! ● 27th of July,
                        2020</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">
                    dahliaOS is finally listed on the Distrowatch waiting list!
                    Please visit the site linked below and recommend dahliaOS by clicking "Reccomend" next to our
                    listing!
                    You can use CTRL + F to find us, we're under the "Projects waiting evaluation" list!
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
                    <a class="mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect"
                        href="https://distrowatch.com/dwres.php?resource=submit#search:~:text=dahliaOS%20(submitted%20on%202020%2D07%2D26)">
                        View on Distrowatch
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="dahliaOS-tablet dahliaOS-screen">
            <div class="demo-card-square mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
                <div class="mdl-card__title mdl-card--expand" style="background:
                  url('{{asset "images/update1.png"}}') center left 15% no-repeat #ff3d00;">
                    <h2 class="mdl-card__title-text">Release ● dahliaOS Linux-Based build 200630.1 ● 30th of June, 2020
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">
                    We've released a new version of our Linux-Based builds!
                    This build adds many new features and updates the Pangolin Desktop Environment!
                    Remember, this is an alpha Pre-Release and should not be used in production!
                    Download it below!
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
                    <a class="mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect"
                        href="https://github.com/dahlia-os/releases/releases/tag/200630.1-x86_64">
                        View on Github
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="dahliaOS-tablet dahliaOS-screen">
            <div class="demo-card-square mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
                <div class="mdl-card__title mdl-card--expand" style="background:
                      url('{{asset "images/gradient.png"}}') bottom right 15% no-repeat #ff3d00;">
                    <h2 class="mdl-card__title-text">We've been featured in an article! ● 29th of June, 2020</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">

                    4 weeks ago, an article was published called Top Linux Distributions To Look Forward To In 2020 and
                    we're listed as the number 8 in it!
                    It's exciting for us to see that we're getting some reviews and features in articles, we hope you're
                    as excited as we are!
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
                    <a class="mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect"
                        href="https://www.tecmint.com/new-linux-distributions/">
                        Read on tecmint
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>




        <div class="dahliaOS-tablet dahliaOS-screen">
            <div class="demo-card-square mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
                <div class="mdl-card__title mdl-card--expand" style="background:
                          url('{{asset "images/screenshots/02.png"}}') top right 15% no-repeat #ff3d00;">
                    <h2 class="mdl-card__title-text">Release ● Pangolin web build & domain ● 29th of June, 2020</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">

                    We've released a new update for the online version of Pangolin and ported it over to our custom
                    domain!
                    The web build from now on will automatically update itself so make sure to stay updated!
                    P.S You can also download it as PWA from the website for offline usage.
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
                    <a class="mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect"
                        href="https://web.dahliaos.io/">
                        Try the web demo
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="dahliaOS-tablet dahliaOS-screen">
            <div class="demo-card-square mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
                <div class="mdl-card__title mdl-card--expand" style="background:
                              url('{{asset "images/screenshots/old.png"}}') top left 15% no-repeat #ff3d00;color:#ffffff;">
                    <h2 class="mdl-card__title-text">Release ● Linux build 200614.1 ● 15th of June, 2020</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">

                    This release now features the Pangolin UI! Simply log in and follow the prompt on boot to start the
                    GUI to use Pangolin, or interact with the system through a command line. This build does not run in
                    QEMU and has very limited support in Virtualbox.
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
                    <a class="mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect"
                        href="https://github.com/dahlia-os/releases/releases/tag/200614.1-x86_64">
                        view on github
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="dahliaOS-tablet dahliaOS-screen">
            <div class="demo-card-square mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
                <div class="mdl-card__title mdl-card--expand" style="background:#7289DA;color:#ffffff;">
                    <h2 class="mdl-card__title-text">Community ● 200 Discord members! ● 15th of June, 2020</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">


                    Hello, community members and supporters! We have finally gained 200 members on our Discord server!
                    We appreciate every single one of you showing up and we hope that you'll stick around long enough
                    untill we release the first fully working build of our OS!



                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
                    <a class="mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect"
                        href="https://discord.gg/jwgS3t6">
                        Join our discord
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="dahliaOS-tablet dahliaOS-screen">
            <div class="demo-card-square mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
                <div class="mdl-card__title mdl-card--expand" style="background:
                                      url('{{asset "images/screenshots/old.png"}}') top left 15% no-repeat #ff3d00;color:#ffffff;">
                    <h2 class="mdl-card__title-text">Release ● Pangolin Flutter Web Build ● 12th of June, 2020.</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">

                    We've released a new update for the online version of Pangolin, meant for those who don't want to
                    mess around with Flutter commands, and compiled directly from the latest source!

                    P.S You can also download it as PWA from the website for offline usage
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
                    <a class="mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect"
                        href="https://nmcain.github.io/dahlia/pangolin">
                        Try online
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>



        <div class="dahliaOS-tablet dahliaOS-screen">
            <div class="demo-card-square mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
                <div class="mdl-card__title mdl-card--expand" style="background:
                                           #1DA1F2;color:#ffffff;">
                    <h2 class="mdl-card__title-text">Community ● We're on Twitter! ● 11th of June, 2020.</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">

                    We opened a Twitter account just today!
                    It would mean a lot to us if you went over to check it and leave a follow!

                    We'll be posting a lot of cool stuff over there as we already do on our other social media
                    platforms, listed below! We will be posting new releases there soon!
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
                    <a class="mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect"
                        href="https://twitter.com/realdahliaos">
                        Visit us on Twitter
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="dahliaOS-tablet dahliaOS-screen">
            <div class="demo-card-square mdl-card mdl-shadow--2dp">
                <div class="mdl-card__title mdl-card--expand" style="background:
                                              url('{{asset "images/gradient.png"}}') bottom right 15% no-repeat #ff3d00;">
                    <h2 class="mdl-card__title-text">Development ● New user interfaces! ● 11th of June, 2020.</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__supporting-text">
                    We are starting work on two new user shells called Starlight and Haven!
                    Starlight and Haven UIs will be more of a modern, simple, minimalistic design, different than
                    Pangolin's material style design.
                    The new interfaces will follow a new design metaphor!


                </div>
                <div class="mdl-card__actions mdl-card--border">
                    <a class="mdl-button mdl-button--colored mdl-js-button mdl-js-ripple-effect"
                        href="https://github.com/dahlia-os/starlight">
                        View on Github
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>



    </div>
</div>
<div id="features" class="dahliaOS-wear-section">
    <div class="dahliaOS-wear-band">
        <div class="dahliaOS-wear-band-text">
            <div class="sulphurpoint mdl-typography--display-2 mdl-typography--font-thin">Just the basics</div>
            <p class="mdl-typography--headline mdl-typography--font-thin">
                dahliaOS keeps things light by only including apps you need, and you can add all of your favorites from
                other operating systems using the Containers app. dahliaOS also provides a curated marketplace for
                third-party native Flutter applications, so you can use nearly every application within one system!.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="mdl-typography--font-regular mdl-typography--text-uppercase dahliaOS-alt-link"
                    href="https://github.com/dahlia-os/pangolin-desktop/tree/master/lib/applications">
                    Browse apps&nbsp;<i class="material-icons">chevron_right</i>
                </a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="dahliaOS-customized-section">
    <div class="dahliaOS-customized-section-text">
        <div class="mdl-typography--font-light mdl-typography--display-1-color-contrast">A wide range of supported
            devices</div>
        <p class="mdl-typography--font-light">
            dahliaOS provides a fast and stable experience on nearly every computer, from a 2004 desktop tower to the
            latest generation of mobile notebooks. Our dual kernel approach allows users with new(er) hardware to take
            advantage of the Zircon Kernel, while maintaining support for older devices using the Linux Kernel.
            <br>
            <a href="https://github.com/dahlia-os/documentation/blob/master/supported-hardware.md"
                class="dahliaOS-link mdl-typography--font-light">View supported devices</a>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="dahliaOS-customized-section-image"></div>
</div>
